<%= stylesheet_link_tag "back-partners-comm", :media => "all"  %>   
<% @title = "CGT Partners Page Back - Our Partners Comment" -%>
<% @header = "CGT Partners Page Back - Our Partners Comment" -%>
<div id="block-mgt">    
  <%= render(:partial => 'menu') %>    
  <div id="operate-mgt">
    <div id="operate-intro">
      <h3>Information About Our Partners Comment</h3>
      <p>It shows brief of CGT partners. The box size is totally 142 lettersX4 lines (568 letters), but the 3 lines of them are for the brief, and the last line is for the contact email. Its font size is 12px and its content is text.
      
      <p>In this page, there is only a operation - New Comment. If there is not any comment (blank) in it, click the operation to add a new comment. Otherwise, use the operaion to update it.
      <p>Please review the comment as follows.
      </p>
    </div><!-- end #operate-intro -->

    <div id="operate-area">
      <h3>Show Our Partners Comment</h3>
      <h5>(The show box size is the same to Our Partners Comment.)</h5>
       <% if @partner %>
      <div id="operate-show">
        <p><%= @partner.content %></p>
      </div>
      <div id="operate-author">
        <h5>Current Author:  </h5> 
      </div>
      <div id="operate-author">     
        <p><%= @partner.author %></p>
      </div>
      <div id="operate-author">
        <h5>Current Contact Email:  </h5> 
      </div>
      <div id="operate-author">     
        <p><%= @partner.email %></p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="operate-admin">
        <h5>Current Admin: </h5> 
      </div>    
      <div id="operate-admin">
        <p>DerDer</p>
      </div>
      
       <% else %>

      <div id="operate-show">
        <p></p>
      </div>
      <div id="operate-author">
        <h5>Current Author:  </h5> 
      </div>
